{"tid":741702,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"咩原因去自殺先可以接受？","createTime":"2018-07-14T02:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T16:52:44.000Z","uid":179902,"like":31,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8b2a7043f5be82b0ae3c34aa4d2ae1de8a452cf4","tid":741702,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得係因病厭世，例如癌症去到末期，周身都痛落唔到床，又成日嘔，甚至可能要插鼻胃管餵食。如果已經處理晒生後事，我覺得以自殺（即係安樂死）去消除不可逆轉嘅痛苦係可以接受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而其他因爲感情問題、學業壓力而去自殺，我會覺得好可惜，因為呢類問題都係短期問題，只要捱得過就會無事。何況世界咁大，咁多風景、人物都未睇未認識，自殺唔會好浪費咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇？"},{"pid":"02fa0a08164e113cbcde80c2cc9c6c895c51e175","tid":741702,"uid":132587,"like":42,"dislike":7,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"活係宜家既香港"},{"pid":"10b8b84e4a3bcab5ee98954aa8b437e79b682e07","tid":741702,"uid":78791,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99358e996fddfaa1574084fde8d0533fbda13f5e","tid":741702,"uid":151904,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"咩原因都可以接受<br />\n因為係佢自己嘅選擇<br />\n我冇權去judge"},{"pid":"c1cd5f3177c72544de8d58428ef7b8bb6d09e45a","tid":741702,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">條問題應該轉做<br />\n因咩自殺唔會令你覺得佢on9 </span>"},{"pid":"5a7a871748c8746eee146024fedf34d2a5ab2d3b","tid":741702,"uid":161731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:16:33.000Z","msg":"窮"},{"pid":"ef0bb2de06caa4c90066bcd4011bf08dc5540136","tid":741702,"uid":13667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"個人認為 冇傷害到人的情況下 就可以 包括其他親人朋友感受"},{"pid":"1c7658876e9f6dd571f5c0ee4938d0844542f61c","tid":741702